{"tid":2082031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新世代拋棄港股 券商SoFi︰八成用戶買美股","createTime":"2020-06-27T16:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T17:25:22.000Z","uid":1086,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3c053c5d7fee5b7d4b2c7fdef3726d3fc891fe94","tid":2082031,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"前身為8 securities近月被收購後改名SoFi Hong Kong，集團以港、美股零佣金作招徠，吸引後生仔入場投資，SoFi高級副總裁（國際）Mathias Helleu表示，公司逾6成客戶為18至30歲，平均年齡低於35歲，對比整個香港投資客戶年齡層屬於非常年輕。<br />\n<br />\nSoFi透露今年第一季用戶較上季增長高達4倍，其間集團沒有增加宣傳，Mathias Helleu相信是因為美股近期的波幅較大，更能吸引投資者。平台同時提供港、美兩地股市買賣，數據則反映香港用戶在近4個月大舉進軍美股，<span style=\"color: red;\">由1月美、港股比例為44比56，大幅攀升至6月的80比20。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>散戶至愛大牌子</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n美國散戶瘋狂追捧股價低殘的航空股，香港亦有部份相同的情況，SoFi透露3月底大市見底至6月中其間，單按買盤成交量計，最多的依次為波音（BA）、Tesla（TSLA）及三倍反向追蹤納指ETF（SQQQ）。而整個3月冧市其間平台的交易量亦都大幅增加，高峯時期成交一度多過平時的兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n至於散戶買美股用甚麼買賣策略，Mathias Helleu分析就指SoFi用戶其實大部份為長揸藍籌的客户﹔其次是2至3星期短炒﹔而Day trade即日買賣就最少。當然按交易量而言，即日交易的客戶貢獻較大，故此不難見到波音及SQQQ買盤量最多。<br />\n<br />\n按照SoFi的數據，最受散戶歡迎的仍是經典的美股藍籌，如亞馬遜（AMZN）、蘋果（AAPL）、Tesla、微軟（MSFT）。而事後睇亦都證明散戶眼光準確，Tesla由3月中低位起計升幅高達187%，亞馬遜及蘋果皆升近七成至創新高，穩陣之餘收穫豐富。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200626/A2VNWKNINMEICKNVH3LZ5W2WHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200626%2FA2VNWKNINMEICKNVH3LZ5W2WHE%2F&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=b03c89d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200626%2FA2VNWKNINMEICKNVH3LZ5W2WHE%2F&h=4afd1daa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200626/A2VNWKNINMEICKNVH3LZ5W2WHE/</a>"},{"pid":"479e5756534727f6213826ca82a2c164f7643a8b","tid":2082031,"uid":97078,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"捱到下個周期 唔好margin 就贏"},{"pid":"69cc514014d730bf4d0b550aed6589b1d738168d","tid":2082031,"uid":241504,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"survivorship bias<br />\nsofi咁渣都用=&gt;用戶低能"},{"pid":"ccc25aa23226ec08a6477e101feb68153054a65e","tid":2082031,"uid":241504,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"69cc514014d730bf4d0b550aed6589b1d738168d","tid":2082031,"uid":241504,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"survivorship bias<br />\nsofi咁渣都用=&gt;用戶低能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"coclusion:<br />\n新世代低能優散拋棄港股"},{"pid":"f0d17edd638ff05e407c1b544189126b5b7fcef4","tid":2082031,"uid":1086,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"69cc514014d730bf4d0b550aed6589b1d738168d","tid":2082031,"uid":241504,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"survivorship bias<br />\nsofi咁渣都用=&gt;用戶低能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"美股一通,好似人要方便又唔想俾牛牛果2蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ec300e02ad8155fcef393a1a3f4ea8356ae981","tid":2082031,"uid":277186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"我hsbc個倉打算轉走哂佢 係咪可以射倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想賣出又買入"},{"pid":"a9024561ae96fe492e31b2feb48e56834b3d8076","tid":2082031,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"SOFI 定 IB 好d"},{"pid":"a888193a774df9aae819617b09c355e46fe49525","tid":2082031,"uid":25316,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"SQQQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e099e2c331fd08afc59981c095bab3a6e2aba86","tid":2082031,"uid":278097,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"致富個apps換美金都唔知咩牌價"},{"pid":"7ed39a5c7bc376ec87b117e6fafadd673a339618","tid":2082031,"uid":1086,"like":1,"d